  <Collapse title='最近在忙什么'>
    学习技术栈,然后找实习ing...
  </Collapse>

  {/* about-blog */}
  <h2 id='about-blog'>About Blog</h2>
  <p>Website history:</p>
  <Timeline
    events={[
      {
        date: '2026-04-18',
        content:
          '发现绝美主题 <a href="https://github.com/cworld1/astro-theme-pure" target="_blank">Astro Theme Pure</a>,于是决定搭建个人博客，记录生活和学习的点滴.'
